<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2010/07/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>SharedProperties</id>
    <version>0.0.1</version>
    <title>Shared C# Project Properties</title>
    <summary>Allows specifying shared project properties at the solution level.</summary>
    <authors>shuruev</authors>
    <description>Introduced Shared.props file at the solution level, which can be used to specify massive changes to all the projects within a solution.
Commonly used scenarios:
- specify assembly signing properties using the same *.snk file
- set CopyLocal to False for certain references
- enforce the same StyleCop or FxCop rules across the solution
- etc.

Feel free to contribute your use case so it could be added to usage examples.</description>
